The Todo Academy, the setting for the broadcast series Tenjho Tenge (2004), was created to revive Tokugawa era martial arts: it's a high school of brawling thugs, ruled by a student "executive council."    The Imperial match tournament has begun and the natural pair of Mitsuomi and Maya are more than enough to create a name for the Juken Club.
 Meanwhile, Dogen Takayanagi and Fu Chen continue their plans for the birth of the true warrior and, in so doing, unleash the deadly Dragon's Eye residing in Shin, a mistake that will forever alter Shin's friendship with Mitsuomi.
